      </p>
    </header>

    <nav class="toc">
      <strong>Contents</strong>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#what-youre-building">What you're building</a></li>
        <li><a href="#prerequisites">Prerequisites</a></li>
        <li><a href="#what-is-mcp">What MCP actually does</a></li>
        <li><a href="#setup">Project setup</a></li>
        <li><a href="#first-tool">Your first tool</a></li>
        <li><a href="#more-tools">Adding more tools</a></li>
        <li><a href="#resources">Adding a resource</a></li>
        <li><a href="#testing">Testing with MCP Inspector</a></li>
